reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best nonstick pan value on Amazon!
reviews.reviewText: These nonstick pans are amazing. I was looking for three diverse size pots with lids which has been hard to find. These are lightweight, were easy to assemble and have a beautiful color. I use these every day and they heat quickly, cook wonderfully and are easy to clean. I highly recommend them. You won’t be disappointed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These pans are amazing. I moved to Italy a few years ago. When I arrived to my new house I found out I couldn’t use my pans because the stove was an induction stove. So I had to shop around for induction cookware. I ended up purchasing very expensive Italian induction cookware and only lasted a few weeks and the nonstick feature was gone, the pans burnt, and were unserviceable as all the food stuck to the surface and burned. When I visited the USA I went and bought new pans from a very recognized brand, and again, they only lasted a month and became unserviceable. I had family coming to visit me from the USA and I didn’t want them to see my ugly pans. So I started looking around for new induction cookware and I came across these amazing pans. The price was very reasonable, and considerably cheaper than the previous pans I had purchased. I read the great reviews and decided to give them a try. I received them very quickly, I had them now for over 3 months and they still look like new, they are awesome to cook any food, the food doesn’t stick, and they look amazing. I received many compliments about how nice they look and how good they are to cook the food. I am extremely please with these pans, and I am looking at exploring and purchasing more products from this company. I recommend these pans!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased an induction range and my old non-stick pans did not work. I ordered these and they are great. Would buy again.
